    <USER_MESSAGE_FROM_NATIVE>Y</USER_MESSAGE_FROM_NATIVE>
    <USER_MESSAGE>Examine this Pentaho ktr or kjb file and provide three items: 
1) A concise summary of the steps performed and your assessment of the function of the ktr or kjb
2) A list of all of the data sources or targets found in the file, including databases and files
3) A note about any SQL statements that are included in the job or transformation and any potential issues migrating from Cloudera Hive to Amazon EMR Hive for the SQL used</USER_MESSAGE>
    <USER_MESSAGE_FROM_STREAM/>
    <SYSTEM_MESSAGE>You are an expert in Pentaho Data Integration KTR and KJB files.</SYSTEM_MESSAGE>
